CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782911913
OL,3,CTom Kerridge: Cutting VAT crucial to
OL,4,Csave hundreds of pubs, restaurants &
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FChef Tom Kerridge said lowering the
OL,8,FVAT rate for hospitality was the
OL,9,Fsingle most important thing the
OL,10,FGovernment could do to support local
OL,11,Fpubs, restaurants, cafes and hotels.
OL,13,FThe publican and restauranteur warned
OL,14,Fhundreds more businesses could close
OL,15,Funless the VAT rate was halved to ten
OL,16,Fper cent.
OL,18,FIt's estimated around 21 businesses
OL,19,Fare going bust each week because their
OL,20,Fbills are too big.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782911913
OL,3,CTom Kerridge: Cutting VAT crucial to
OL,4,Csave hundreds of pubs, restaurants &
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FKerridge said reducing the rate would
OL,8,Fhelp long term investment growth and
OL,9,Fget more people into work.
OL,11,F"This is about long term investment
OL,12,Fgrowth, we all know that if 21
OL,13,Fbusinesses are shutting per week,
OL,14,Fthat's revenue that comes to the
OL,15,FExchequer, that's disappearing, that
OL,16,Fthere isn't any growth", Tom Kerridge
OL,17,Fsaid.
OL,19,F"The rest of the hospitality is
OL,20,Fstagnant or moving backwards.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782911913
OL,3,CTom Kerridge: Cutting VAT crucial to
OL,4,Csave hundreds of pubs, restaurants &
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"There's no youth employment and lots
OL,8,Fof issues further down the line
OL,9,Fimpacting on the supply chain from
OL,10,Ffisheries, farming, agriculture,
OL,11,Feverything that comes into hospitality.
OL,13,F"We all know that hospitality is
OL,14,Factually the lifeblood and the
OL,15,Fcultural hub of so many places in
OL,16,Fsociety.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782911913
OL,3,CTom Kerridge: Cutting VAT crucial to
OL,4,Csave hundreds of pubs, restaurants &
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,F"When you see town planners
OL,8,Frejuvenating city centres, the first
OL,9,Fdrawings that they do, cafes, bars,
OL,10,Fpubs, clubs, restaurants, nightlife,
OL,11,Fthat is all so equally important about
OL,12,Fgrowth.
OL,14,F"And no businesses are run by the
OL,15,Faccountants.
OL,17,F"The accountants and the spreadsheets
OL,18,Fare there, they help guide business,
OL,19,Fits operators and it's operators that
OL,20,Funderstand the use of investment for
OL,21,Fgrowth," he explained.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
