PN,37905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782911913
OL,3,CTom Kerridge: Cutting VAT crucial to
OL,4,Csave hundreds of pubs, restaurants &
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FTom Kerridge is best known for
OL,8,Ftransforming traditional British pub
OL,9,Ffood into Michelin-starred dining and
OL,10,Fbuilt a reputation as one of the UK's
OL,11,Fmost influential modern chefs.
OL,13,FThe 52-year-old wants a million people
OL,14,Fto sign his Vats The Problem petition
OL,15,Fto help the high street and support
OL,16,Flocal jobs.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782911913
OL,3,CTom Kerridge: Cutting VAT crucial to
OL,4,Csave hundreds of pubs, restaurants &
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FA spokesperson for the Treasury said
OL,8,Fthe government had "the right economic
OL,9,Fplan," adding: "We're backing
OL,10,Fhospitality by cutting VAT on family
OL,11,Fattractions and kids meals this
OL,12,Fsummer, reforming business rates, with
OL,13,Fa #4.3bn support package to limit
OL,14,Fbills rises, capping Corporation Tax
OL,15,Fat 25%, extending World Cup opening
OL,16,Fhours, and taking action on the cost
OL,17,Fof living to boost the sector."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782911913
OL,3,CTom Kerridge: Cutting VAT crucial to
OL,4,Csave hundreds of pubs, restaurants &
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FBut Kerridge said it wasn't enough.
OL,8,FAsked what would happen if there was
OL,9,Fno change in VAT he said: "The
OL,10,Fcontinuation of 21 businesses shutting
OL,11,Fin per week. It doesn't stop, it just
OL,12,Fcontinues slowly, slowly dying before
OL,13,Fit all peters out and disappears.
OL,15,FAnd then that's a society problem,
OL,16,Fthat's a culturally unhappy space for
OL,17,Fus all to be in.
OL,19,F"There's no growth, there's no
OL,20,Fcreativity, there's no movement.
OL,21,FEverything starts going backwards."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/8
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
