CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782911913
OL,3,CTom Kerridge: Cutting VAT crucial to
OL,4,Csave hundreds of pubs, restaurants &
OL,5,Chotels
OL,7,FThe UK has one of the highest VAT
OL,8,Frates in Europe at 20% compared to 10%
OL,9,Fin France, Spain and Italy and 7% in
OL,10,FGermany. Only Denmark is higher.
